WEBVTT

00:00:03.927 --> 00:00:08.515
TAPE FOUR MRS GOLDA HEIMICH. me hot zikh gefunen in in Minchen.

00:00:07.690 --> 00:00:13.255
Kleyn Minchen hot es geheysn, dos iz gevezn nebn Zaltsburg, in Estraykh.

00:00:13.255 --> 00:00:16.003
fun dort hot men undz genumen mit TRUCKS,

00:00:16.009 --> 00:00:17.285
oyf Minchen.

00:00:17.697 --> 00:00:20.408
dos iz ge- a shtot fun Daytshland.

00:00:20.447 --> 00:00:25.388
un dortn hot men undz arayngefirt, dos iz oykh geven a plats

00:00:25.388 --> 00:00:29.059
vu dort hot men registrirt mentshn fun iberol.

00:00:29.059 --> 00:00:34.011
dos iz geven Funkasern hot es geheysn, dos iz geven a groyse militerishe plats

00:00:34.011 --> 00:00:35.226
bay di daytshn.

00:00:35.226 --> 00:00:38.179
un d- dort hot men nokh dem, nokh di milkhome,

00:00:38.179 --> 00:00:51.443
dort mentshn vos zey zenen gekumen fun iberol vos iz gevezn, hot men dort arayngefirt, dort hot gemakht A LOT a sakh di ADMINISTRATION zakhn, vu ven vos, vu men zol firn yedn eynem,

00:00:51.443 --> 00:01:01.703
un dort ze'mir undz geven beerekh tsvey vokhn. dort iz geven zeyer gut, dort hot men gegebn esn, s'geven kosher esn un ales vos m'hot gevolt,

00:01:01.703 --> 00:01:03.129
farshidene zakhn.

00:01:03.129 --> 00:01:10.745
un me hot oykh gekent nemen roye, ober undz ho'mir genumen, s'geven farleslekh, mentshn.

00:01:11.511 --> 00:01:14.250
fun dort hot men undz gefirt oyf

00:01:14.250 --> 00:01:19.034
Poking-Valdshtat. dos iz gevezn a fli-plats,

00:01:19.034 --> 00:01:20.972
nisht vayt fun Paso,

00:01:20.978 --> 00:01:25.123
iz dos iz geven a fli-plats far di daytshe militer,

00:01:25.197 --> 00:01:28.214
dos iz geven a zeyer a groyse plats,

00:01:28.214 --> 00:01:33.403
dortn iz gevezn tsen toyznt mentshn nokh di milkhome

00:01:33.403 --> 00:01:38.752
fun iberol, fun di gantse velt zenen gekumen mentshn dortn. ales vos hot gevolt

00:01:38.752 --> 00:01:42.887
ergets forn, o kumen, geyn. dort iz oykh geven a plats vos,

00:01:42.887 --> 00:01:47.080
dos iz geven azoy aroys fun shtot, o tomer hot gedorfn epes

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:50.565
hot men gedorfn forn mit a BUS oyf beerekh a halbe sho,

00:01:50.565 --> 00:01:52.648
arayn in di shtetl Poking,

00:01:52.648 --> 00:01:55.919
d- dos plats aleyn hot geheysn Poking-Valdshtat.

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:58.884
dort ze'mir gevezn tsvey yor,

00:01:58.884 --> 00:02:02.923
mayn man hot gearbet, dos hot geheysn dort Vad Hadati,

00:02:02.929 --> 00:02:04.711
di di rabinat.

00:02:04.853 --> 00:02:06.419
un dortn

00:02:06.419 --> 00:02:08.781
ho'mir undz

00:02:08.781 --> 00:02:13.304
ge- gevezn, se gants gut gevezn, s'gevezn azolkhe blokn,

00:02:13.304 --> 00:02:16.086
zikh gut bakent dort mit a sakh mentshn,

00:02:16.210 --> 00:02:19.427
un fun dort ze'mir undz geforn

00:02:19.450 --> 00:02:21.334
oyf Pariz.

00:02:22.217 --> 00:02:23.257
kinder?

00:02:23.027 --> 00:02:27.015
yo, undz ho'mir gehat shoyn demolts der zun iz geboyrn

00:02:27.015 --> 00:02:31.374
in nayntsn zeks un fertsik, in september fertsn,

00:02:31.735 --> 00:02:34.229
un der klenere zun,

00:02:33.613 --> 00:02:34.642
in Poking.

00:02:34.229 --> 00:02:36.757
yo, in Poking-Valdshtat, hot gevezn a,

00:02:35.880 --> 00:02:37.484
vi heyst er?

00:02:37.101 --> 00:02:38.962
er heyst Mendl.

00:02:38.962 --> 00:02:40.808
Menachem Yosef.

00:02:40.915 --> 00:02:43.864
un der tsveyter zun Yeshie

00:02:43.864 --> 00:02:45.434
iz geboyrn

00:02:45.434 --> 00:02:47.779
draytsn monat shpeter,

00:02:47.779 --> 00:02:51.711
JUST nokh yomkiper, dray tog nokh yomkiper,

00:02:51.711 --> 00:02:55.913
iz dortn undz ho'mir shoyn gehat demolts tsvey kleyne kinder,

00:02:55.913 --> 00:02:59.187
un undz ho'mir genumen a BUS,

00:02:59.187 --> 00:03:05.175
vos hot undz gefirt oyf Minchen, vayl undz ze'mir nisht geven in Minchen take, in a bisl vayter.

00:03:05.586 --> 00:03:10.097
un do- undz ze'mir ge- fun dort o- ze'mir geforn

00:03:10.097 --> 00:03:12.296
oyf Pariz mit a ban.

00:03:11.998 --> 00:03:15.265
far vos hostu oysgekloybn Pariz?

00:03:14.631 --> 00:03:17.944
vayl undz ho'mir gehat papirn

00:03:17.944 --> 00:03:20.193
tsu forn oyf Tshile.

00:03:21.111 --> 00:03:28.423
nor mayn man iz nisht geven azoy zeyer tsufridn, er zogt az dos iz amerikane land, ikh veys vos,

00:03:28.423 --> 00:03:31.022
ze'mir undz koydem geblibn in Pariz.

00:03:31.022 --> 00:03:33.755
iz dort iz zeyer gut gevezn, mayn man

00:03:33.755 --> 00:03:39.442
hot bakumen, di di mentshn vos zenen gekumen v- JUST normal andere mentshn

00:03:39.442 --> 00:03:42.379
hobn gedorfn geyn arbetn un fardinen dortn,

00:03:42.379 --> 00:03:50.282
ober dey velkhe zenen geven rabonim, dey hot men oysgehaltn fun Amerike. Ikhad Harabonim hot es geheysn.

00:03:50.389 --> 00:03:55.541
undz ze'mir dort gevezn, se geven gants gut, undz ho'mir zikh platsirt dortn

00:03:55.541 --> 00:03:56.866
in a hotel,

00:03:56.866 --> 00:04:04.676
se geven a yidisher balbos fun Erets Yisroel, a hotel, a zeyer sheyne hotel, dort hot men nor gekent araynkumen mit kinder.

00:04:04.868 --> 00:04:07.978
un der bruder, mayn man's hot oykh gevoynt dortn,

00:04:07.978 --> 00:04:09.451
dort iz gevezn

00:04:09.627 --> 00:04:14.379
z- tsvey mol tsi zeks shtokn aroyf tsu geyn, eyn zayt un di tsveyte zayt.

00:04:15.212 --> 00:04:20.184
un dortn hot men gekent zen vos mentshn zenen.

00:04:20.916 --> 00:04:24.048
dort hot men zikh bekent mit mentshn

00:04:24.122 --> 00:04:27.005
fayne, dos mitele,

00:04:27.005 --> 00:04:28.183
ALL SORTS.

00:04:29.505 --> 00:04:32.975
undz ze'mir ongekumen dort mit tsvey kleyne kinder,

00:04:33.893 --> 00:04:38.308
iz ho'mir bakumen koydem oyfn zekstn shtok a tsimer.

00:04:39.124 --> 00:04:42.302
nu, kokhn hot men nisht getort,

00:04:42.302 --> 00:04:44.434
vayl se geven fayer geferlekh.

00:04:44.710 --> 00:04:46.673
iz gevezn untn,

00:04:46.673 --> 00:04:49.474
untn in di GROUND FLOOR,

00:04:49.474 --> 00:04:51.943
iz gevezn kokh, a kokh.

00:04:52.388 --> 00:04:54.424
dort iz gevezn azoy.

00:04:55.577 --> 00:04:57.607
tsu fir oyvns,

00:04:57.607 --> 00:04:59.115
tsu tsvey,

00:04:59.323 --> 00:05:02.084
dos iz geven far di mentshn tsu kokhn.

00:05:02.479 --> 00:05:04.863
un khuts dem iz gevezn

00:05:04.863 --> 00:05:13.712
eyn eyvele mit tsvey fayerkes far kinder, vayl se geven algemeyn nor kinder hobn gekent dort araynkumen, nor mit kinder.

00:05:13.836 --> 00:05:17.081
iz dortn hot men nisht getort

00:05:17.081 --> 00:05:23.128
leygn gornisht, vayl az s'kumt emetser arop kokhn a kashe zol es zayn fray.

00:05:23.286 --> 00:05:27.291
ober dos iz nor ge- geven geshribn dortn ergets

00:05:27.291 --> 00:05:29.574
ober dos iz nisht geven azoy,

00:05:29.580 --> 00:05:34.535
mentshn zenen gegangen un hobn avekgeshtelt fish un farshidene zakhn,

00:05:34.643 --> 00:05:39.581
un az yener hot gekumen un hot gedarfn kokhn far di BABY,

00:05:39.688 --> 00:05:48.831
iz vos hot er gekent tun? hot avekgeshtelt in di zayt, un zi iz gekumen mit a gevald, az vos hostu getun? host avekgeshtelt dem kalye vern!

00:05:48.831 --> 00:06:03.948
zogt zi, keyner hot dir nisht geheysn dort avekshteln oyf di kinder fayer. di kinder fayer iz SPECIAL vegn dem, du farshteyst aleyn, a pitsele kind fun a por monat ken men nisht zogn az emetser kokht fish un ikh derken nisht makhn dayn kashe.

00:06:04.107 --> 00:06:10.178
dort iz geven geferlekh, se iz zeyer zeyer shvere matsev gevezn oyf azoy fil

00:06:10.178 --> 00:06:14.833
az koydem ho'mir gevoynt oyfn fiftn shtok ober nisht lang.

00:06:15.109 --> 00:06:18.261
di, undz ho'mir gehat a mazl,

00:06:18.261 --> 00:06:26.510
mayn man hot noyse kheyn bay di MISSES vos zi hot geven di MANAGERke dort, se iz geven a poylishe froy,

00:06:26.989 --> 00:06:28.603
MISSES Kenter,

00:06:28.947 --> 00:06:36.081
un ir man hot gear- hot geven in di milkhome in ⟨Anders Armeivshn⟩, hot ir shoyn gehert? dos iz azoy geven

00:06:36.081 --> 00:06:37.853
di poylishe mentshn

00:06:37.853 --> 00:06:40.314
zenen oykh geven kegn di daytshn.

00:06:40.590 --> 00:06:45.953
un zi hot gefirt dortn, un er, zi hot ge- zeyer

00:06:45.953 --> 00:06:53.142
ge- mayn man hot ir z- zeyer gefoln oyf azoy fil az vos er hot gebetn

00:06:53.142 --> 00:06:55.184
hot zi nokh gegebn far im.

00:06:55.184 --> 00:07:05.678
un gezogt az her, mit tsvey pitselekh kinder oyfn fiftn shtok, m'darf geyn in untn in di kokh kokhn, dos iz farshteystu dokh aleyn az dos iz nisht azoy gring.

00:07:05.700 --> 00:07:19.565
iz zi gegangen in tsvey vokhn, o zi hot oykh nisht gekent aroysvarfn keynem vayl yeder shtub iz geven farnumen, ober ven zi hot nor gekent hobn a CHANCE tsu tun epes, hot zi undz gegebn oyfn dritn.

00:07:20.162 --> 00:07:23.956
un dos iz shoyn gevezn a bisl mentshlekh,

00:07:23.956 --> 00:07:27.294
vayl fun dritn shtok iz iz shoyn nisht di zekste.

00:07:27.385 --> 00:07:30.343
iz undz ho'mir bakumen zeyer a sheyne tsimer,

00:07:30.343 --> 00:07:33.161
un nokh dem hot zi undz nokh gegebn,

00:07:33.161 --> 00:07:35.877
dort iz gevezn azolkhe kleyne tsimerlekh,

00:07:35.877 --> 00:07:43.510
vos iz efsher gevezn a STORE ROOM, tsi vos, ikh veys, oyf yedn shtok iz geven azelkhe kleyne tsimerelkh, hot zi undz dos oykhet gegebn.

00:07:44.074 --> 00:07:45.556
ho'mir gehat tsvey tsimern,

00:07:45.556 --> 00:07:48.678
dortn s'geven a bet in dem kleynem tsimer, dort hot men zikh

00:07:48.678 --> 00:07:50.076
gekent leygn,

00:07:50.638 --> 00:07:55.981
un me hot gekent esn dortn, nisht geven tsu fil tuml in di groyse shtub,

00:07:56.798 --> 00:07:59.576
ober ikh hob zikh gemakht a seyder

00:07:59.700 --> 00:08:05.077
un ikh bin gegangen yedn in der fri, bin ikh oyfgeshtanen fri,

00:08:05.202 --> 00:08:08.368
un ikh bin gegangen un ikh hob opgekokht,

00:08:09.589 --> 00:08:11.990
 vos ikh hob gedorfn vashn OR vos,

00:08:11.990 --> 00:08:15.641
hob ikh ales demolts erleydikt, demolts ven mentshn hobn nokh geshlofn,

00:08:16.086 --> 00:08:20.327
un ikh hob zikh opgekokht un yeder eyner hot bakumen

00:08:20.327 --> 00:08:22.610
a eyn a halb sho

00:08:22.701 --> 00:08:26.596
oyf oyf tsu kokhn oder tsu varemen oder vos er hot gevolt

00:08:26.596 --> 00:08:34.761
hot er gekent tun in dem, un ikh hob gebetn oyb zi ken dos makhn azoy mer veyniker mitog shtunde, vayl dort hot men gegesn mitog.

00:08:35.087 --> 00:08:40.728
un di undz ikh hob zikh dos azoy ayngefirt un bay tog

00:08:40.728 --> 00:08:42.669
mayn man gegangen lernen,

00:08:42.669 --> 00:08:47.208
un ikh s'gegangen in di park, dort iz zeyer a sakh parkS in Pariz,

00:08:47.208 --> 00:08:51.520
yeder gegnt hot a park, vayl dort iz nishto keyn hoyf,

00:08:51.520 --> 00:08:52.904
dort yeder eyner

00:08:52.904 --> 00:08:57.831
geyt in mit di kinder in park, ikh hob geshtrikt far zey, farshidene zakhn,

00:08:57.831 --> 00:09:06.758
un zey zey hobn zikh geshpilt, un mitog bin ikh aheym gegangen un mayn man gekumen, un m'hot opgegesn, un nokh mitog hot men gemakht di zelbe zakh, aroysgegangen.

00:09:06.758 --> 00:09:07.717
dort.

00:09:07.217 --> 00:09:11.379
gedenkst di nomen fun park vu du bist geganen mit di kinder?

00:09:12.567 --> 00:09:17.542
di di di METRO STATION hot geheysn Le Shapel.

00:09:17.542 --> 00:09:20.779
iz efsher hot es geheysn oykhet di park azoy.

00:09:21.088 --> 00:09:30.009
undz ze'mir dort gevezn tsvey yor dort. un nokh di tsvey yor iz gekumen der balbos

00:09:30.049 --> 00:09:31.578
fun dem hotel,

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:34.163
un er hot gemakht a gevald,

00:09:34.163 --> 00:09:39.521
m'hot tsu grund geleygt ales vos mentshn hobn nor gekent,

00:09:39.521 --> 00:09:43.880
m'hot oyfgehoybn di CARPET, vayl s'gevorn shmutsik fun di kinder un ikh veys.

00:09:44.055 --> 00:09:47.663
un me hot gemuzt aroysgeyn fun dortn.

00:09:47.663 --> 00:09:51.266
er hot gegebn ultimatum far di Zhoynt,

00:09:51.266 --> 00:09:58.595
az dos zol vern oysgeleydikt un zey zoln im batsoln shadn⟨UNK⟩ epes a groyse groyses gelter.

00:09:58.753 --> 00:10:01.244
vayl s'gevorn in gantsn kaput.

00:10:01.403 --> 00:10:12.399
dort iz gevezn azoy oykhet, m'hot gemakht farshidens un a shul hot men gemakht, dos un yents, a peysekhdike kokh, un dos ales hot men gemakht azoy vi eyner vos iz hefker.

00:10:12.878 --> 00:10:15.555
un shoyn undz ho'mir gemuzt zukhn,

00:10:15.780 --> 00:10:26.541
undz ze'mir nokh alts gezesn in Pariz, s'iz nisht geven azoy gring, do dort, me hot prubirt efsher oyf Amerike, dos ahin, ober s'iz nisht geven azoy glat ales nokh.

00:10:25.115 --> 00:10:26.894
host geklert of Yisroel?

00:10:26.935 --> 00:10:27.756
neyn.

00:10:27.762 --> 00:10:30.197
neyn, dort iz gevezn zeyer nokh nisht,

00:10:30.197 --> 00:10:32.312
nokh gornisht, in fuftsiker yorn.

00:10:33.448 --> 00:10:35.889
iz ze'mir

00:10:36.115 --> 00:10:41.334
ho'mir bazukht a dire, un undz ze'mir ge- gegangen, mir ho'mir getrofn a dire,

00:10:41.334 --> 00:10:43.739
Port Itali, hot es geheysn.

00:10:43.739 --> 00:10:47.528
ober dos in Pariz iz nisht TERRIBLE,

00:10:47.528 --> 00:10:53.442
dey zakhn, forn, kumen, geyn, dort iz di transport zeyer zeyer gut,

00:10:53.442 --> 00:10:58.772
di untererdishe un di BUSES un dos un ale zakhn iz zeyer gring gevezn.

00:10:58.812 --> 00:11:01.255
undz ho'mir zikh genumen dort a dire,

00:11:01.255 --> 00:11:05.921
mayn man iz dort gevorn aza shtikl rov dortn a por mentshn zenen geven dort,

00:11:05.921 --> 00:11:13.182
er hot gedavnt dort far zey, un di k- un s'geven a zeyer a fayne shtibl dortn vu undz ho'mir dort gevoynt eyner,

00:11:13.290 --> 00:11:16.308
un di kinder hobn zikh geshpilt.

00:11:14.441 --> 00:11:16.158
du host gehobt parnose.

00:11:16.308 --> 00:11:25.294
mayn man hot bakumen gelt fun di Ikhud Harabonim, a mol s'gekumen a yontev hot men hobn zey gegebn amerikaner pek, COFFEE mit tsigaret, ikh veys,

00:11:25.294 --> 00:11:26.548
farshidene zakhn.

00:11:26.655 --> 00:11:30.769
un undz ze'mir dort geven un s'geven gants gut.

00:11:30.769 --> 00:11:34.546
ober in nayntsn fuftsik,

00:11:34.806 --> 00:11:38.344
ven Koreo hot ongehoybn tsu makhn kuntsn,

00:11:39.700 --> 00:11:42.169
iz gevorn aza tuml

00:11:42.169 --> 00:11:44.126
dortn in Pariz,

00:11:44.126 --> 00:11:50.901
un yeder eyner hot gemeynt az Eyrope vet zayn in fayer, vet aroyfgeyn,

00:11:50.901 --> 00:11:52.741
un vet gants Eyrope vet geyn.

00:11:52.741 --> 00:11:53.717
FINISHED.

00:11:54.060 --> 00:11:57.348
yeder hot gezukht vu ergets tsu forn.

00:11:57.348 --> 00:12:04.433
vayl az nisht, iz ver veyst vos vet zayn? zey hobn zikh dort geshlogn, ahin, aher, m'hot deys genumen, yents,

00:12:05.130 --> 00:12:11.992
un mayn man iz aheymgekumen, un zogt er, du veyst, m'redt, Rashe shul, hot es geheysn vu er hot gegangen,

00:12:12.218 --> 00:12:18.627
m'redt farshidens fun vos vet do zayn, ver veyst vos vet zayn, un Amerike vet zikh araynmishn, der

00:12:18.627 --> 00:12:20.734
un se se iz nisht azoy zeyer gut.

00:12:21.533 --> 00:12:28.086
un undz flegn'mir, mayn man hot alts gedorfn geyn tsu Zhoynt, m'hot zikh gedorfn meldn,

00:12:28.086 --> 00:12:32.541
yeder khoydesh, prefektur, in di politsey,

00:12:32.541 --> 00:12:34.667
hot men zikh gedorfn meldn, vayl

00:12:34.667 --> 00:12:37.291
oyslender hobn nisht getort arbetn

00:12:37.291 --> 00:12:39.308
un ales gevezn shvarts

00:12:39.308 --> 00:12:41.586
un er hot, m'hot nisht getort

00:12:41.586 --> 00:12:43.653
BUSINESS, o vos

00:12:43.653 --> 00:12:46.226
biz m'hot nisht gehat keyn dire

00:12:46.226 --> 00:12:49.286
in Priz hot men gornisht getort.

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:52.267
vayl demolts iz men nokh geven a a a

00:12:52.267 --> 00:12:53.909
a a TRANSIT.

00:12:53.629 --> 00:12:55.293
REFUGEE.

00:12:54.692 --> 00:12:55.445
yo.

00:12:56.110 --> 00:13:01.841
un er iz aheym gekumen eyn mol fun Zhoynt un er zogt azoy tsu mir, du veyst vos?

00:13:02.202 --> 00:13:06.313
az ikh zits dort un vart un tsvey ire redn zikh dortn,

00:13:06.437 --> 00:13:08.962
un zey zogn, du veyst vos,

00:13:09.306 --> 00:13:11.882
az m'ken forn oyf Oystralye!

00:13:14.503 --> 00:13:17.669
mayn man hot bikhlal nisht gevust v- vu dos iz!

00:13:18.182 --> 00:13:21.838
vu iz dos ergets, vu untern erd dek.

00:13:22.587 --> 00:13:28.996
iz iz er aroyf, yo, du zolst geyn un dort iz do oyfn dritn shtok a meydl,

00:13:28.996 --> 00:13:30.852
vos zi REGISTrirt,

00:13:30.852 --> 00:13:32.671
heyst zi, KOHN EVA.

00:13:33.673 --> 00:13:38.831
iz mayn man gegangen, er hot zikh aroyfgekhapt un gegangen dort ahin tsu ir,

00:13:39.124 --> 00:13:40.319
un

00:13:40.319 --> 00:13:44.231
un er hot gezukht KOHN EVA, un zi zogt, yo, ikh bin dos.

00:13:44.338 --> 00:13:46.073
un vos vilstu?

00:13:46.073 --> 00:13:49.600
zogt er, er vil zikh registrirn oyf Oystralye.

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:55.017
