00:18:12.217 --> 00:18:15.407
vos vos Zhoynt hot nisht azoy gevolt,

00:18:15.407 --> 00:18:18.301
z- m'hot gemakht a shul in eyner fun di tsimern,

00:18:18.301 --> 00:18:21.533
un zey hobn nisht gevolt di ale zakhn makhn vayl

